        <div class="team-badge">
          <div class="team-badge-icon"><i data-lucide="sofa"></i></div>
          <span class="team-badge-text">Interior Fitouts</span>
        </div>
        <div class="team-badge">
          <div class="team-badge-icon"><i data-lucide="wrench"></i></div>
          <span class="team-badge-text">Structural Repair</span>
        </div>
        <div class="team-badge">
          <div class="team-badge-icon"><i data-lucide="building-2"></i></div>
          <span class="team-badge-text">Commercial Construction</span>
        </div>
        <div class="team-badge">
          <div class="team-badge-icon"><i data-lucide="factory"></i></div>
          <span class="team-badge-text">Industrial Projects</span>
        </div>
        <div class="team-badge">
          <div class="team-badge-icon"><i data-lucide="file-check"></i></div>
          <span class="team-badge-text">CMDA &amp; DTCP Support</span>
        </div>
        <div class="team-badge">
          <div class="team-badge-icon"><i data-lucide="package"></i></div>
          <span class="team-badge-text">Turnkey Solutions</span>
        </div>
        <div class="team-badge">
          <div class="team-badge-icon"><i data-lucide="hammer"></i></div>
          <span class="team-badge-text">Building Renovation</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ WHY CHOOSE OUR TEAM ════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section sec-cream" aria-labelledby="why-team-title">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px">
        <span class="section-tag">Why Us</span>
        <h2 class="section-title" id="why-team-title" style="margin:0 auto 12px">Why Choose Our Team</h2>
        <p class="section-sub" style="margin:0 auto;max-width:580px">Every professional in our team is selected for technical competence, client-first attitude, and an uncompromising approach to quality.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-grid reveal">
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-card-icon"><i data-lucide="shield-check"></i></div>
          <h3 class="why-card-title">Engineering Excellence</h3>
          <p class="why-card-text">Every project is led by licensed civil engineers following IS code standards for structural safety and durability.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-card-icon"><i data-lucide="receipt"></i></div>
          <h3 class="why-card-title">Transparent Pricing</h3>
          <p class="why-card-text">Detailed cost breakdowns before work begins — no hidden charges, no surprise escalations at handover.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-card-icon"><i data-lucide="gem"></i></div>
          <h3 class="why-card-title">Premium Materials</h3>
          <p class="why-card-text">Only ISI-certified brands for steel, cement, electrical, and plumbing — sourced from verified suppliers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-card-icon"><i data-lucide="calendar-check"></i></div>
          <h3 class="why-card-title">On-Time Delivery</h3>
          <p class="why-card-text">Milestone-driven schedules tracked weekly by our project manager with real-time progress updates to clients.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-card-icon"><i data-lucide="layers"></i></div>
          <h3 class="why-card-title">End-to-End Management</h3>
          <p class="why-card-text">From design to handover — architecture, structure, interiors, and approvals all handled under one roof.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-card-icon"><i data-lucide="sliders"></i></div>
          <h3 class="why-card-title">Customized Solutions</h3>
          <p class="why-card-text">No two projects are identical. We tailor every design, material choice, and specification to your lifestyle and budget.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-card-icon"><i data-lucide="hard-hat"></i></div>
          <h3 class="why-card-title">Safety Standards</h3>
          <p class="why-card-text">Site safety protocols, PPE compliance, and regular inspections are enforced across all our construction sites.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ COMMITMENT SECTION ════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="commitment-section" aria-labelledby="commitment-title">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:52px;position:relative;z-index:1">
        <span class="section-tag" style="color:var(--gold)">Our Promise</span>
        <h2 class="section-title white" id="commitment-title" style="margin:0 auto 12px">Our Team Commitment</h2>
        <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Five pillars that define how our team approaches every single project — from the first client meeting to the final handover.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="commitment-grid reveal">
        <div class="commitment-card">
          <div class="commitment-icon"><i data-lucide="award"></i></div>
          <div class="commitment-title">Quality Construction</div>
          <div class="commitment-sub">Every stage inspected by our resident engineer. We never compromise on structural integrity.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="commitment-card">
          <div class="commitment-icon"><i data-lucide="heart-handshake"></i></div>
          <div class="commitment-title">Customer Satisfaction</div>
          <div class="commitment-sub">Dedicated client coordinator for every project. Open communication from day one to handover.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="commitment-card">
          <div class="commitment-icon"><i data-lucide="building"></i></div>
          <div class="commitment-title">Structural Excellence</div>
          <div class="commitment-sub">Designed for longevity. RMC concrete, IS steel, and rigorous curing standards on every floor.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="commitment-card">
          <div class="commitment-icon"><i data-lucide="check-circle-2"></i></div>
          <div class="commitment-title">Reliable Execution</div>
          <div class="commitment-sub">Weekly milestone reporting and site visits by senior engineers ensure nothing falls behind schedule.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="commitment-card">
          <div class="commitment-icon"><i data-lucide="lightbulb"></i></div>
          <div class="commitment-title">Innovative Design</div>
          <div class="commitment-sub">3D visualisations and modern design concepts that maximise space, light, and livability.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ CTA SECTION ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="related-services" aria-labelledby="rs-heading">
